{"type": "article", "id": 16154, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2015-10-16T06:41:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 17298, "name": "Yazbukey"}, {"id": 17299, "name": "Fashionary"}, {"id": 17300, "name": "MOAK Studio"}, {"id": 17301, "name": "Beckett Simonon"}, {"id": 17302, "name": "Layer"}, {"id": 17303, "name": "Natascha Madeiski"}, {"id": 17304, "name": "Linnie Mclarty"}, {"id": 9226, "name": "Yves Béhar"}, {"id": 17305, "name": "Emma’s Ontwerpen"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 90, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606140804JT73etXoN1GPAOIW.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\t记事本 by Yazbukey &amp; Fashionary \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t趁着时尚周的热潮， Fashionary 联合法国饰品品牌 Yazbukey 推出了这款记事本。封面就可看到 Yazbukey 经典的大红唇，内页附有与时装相关的小知识和活动资询，时尚字典部分就占到了 20%，是时尚达人必备。售价 28.9 美元，<a href=\"http://fashionary.org/collections/all/products/yazbukey-planner-a5-2016\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>此外，Fashionary 之前与时尚品牌合作的笔记本也都值得借鉴。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112035nrBxVzvMTL1tRkUZ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112036CN7xvRYcZjaXULI9.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112036eS9cpBl1JD7j5iYU.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112037M2okPRLxXh5ncTdz.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112037JEe0TGqu1jbhlg5H.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t “now and then”by Natascha Madeiski&amp; Linnie Mclarty\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是建筑师兼设计师 Natascha Madeiski 和银器匠兼珠宝匠  Linnie Mclarty 的跨界合作。他们分别制作陶瓷容器和金属配件，并巧妙结合成“now and then”的展览。复古造型的陶瓷容器配上有未来感的金属作手柄和勺子显得很独特，似乎保留了物件的大致轮廓，点缀的地方仍然是现代的，是他们向历史和建筑的致敬。容器有灰、粉、绿、白四种颜色和四种造型，它们的展示也像是考古的切面。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112038v5DlayVLg8szjR3u.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112038gwMp97NrSOs4QUib.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112039FjT8uyJvSwLhG1PA.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112039sGfmldbAW4vqFDjO.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.3801956\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112040nAd3a2yWRQKgLJqx.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112040AwmH0dtkQFYWJz3B.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tAugust Access system by Yves Behar\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是一套可以用手机控制门锁的家用系统，包括一个锁，按键盘，内设相机的门铃和配合这个系统的手机 app。使用者可以通过手机控制门锁，即便是不在家的时候，也可以开门放受信任的人进屋，并检查门是否锁上。对于家里有狗或者安排清洁人员进屋是非常方便的。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071120413cSuGXnZNWDjOk4b.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112041gizNb4FfyMPKHScu.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112042i5YtNh7j1ZygCnBq.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112042zQR2Ej64cvNxGlgn.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071120435jSp1F4zt83iw0I9.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.81303419\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tME Dinner by  MOAK Studio &amp; Emma’s Ontwerpen\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是一套饭盒，上下两个碗中间放着一个悬空的架子，碗里放着烧烤架，再外面用皮革固定打包，非常适合出门野餐。两个碗隔着烧烤架叠放就是一个简易的加热保温装置。陶瓷制作的锅上面加了一个木质的盖子，让餐具的整体颜色在柔和中分层变化。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112043jLd4CehGMgaI0Dkn.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071120448tuvZqEjY5NI7SmH.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112044PdAKJme3tqfBzxZp.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112045iZo85YUOwc4IPJd3.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112045vCKQAkUoe3ubzcLY.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tSNEAKERS by Beckett Simonon \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\tBeckett Simonon 成立的目标是提供高品质有个性的鞋，以及可以接受的价格。他们新出的系列就仅仅使用两块正面革（full-grain leather）和未经加工的外底，配合尽可能少的剪裁，却能呈现毫不低价的效果，一共有黑、白、紫红三种颜色，<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/656797549/premium-shoes-for-the-new-breed-of-gentlemen\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112046SU0bKhnGgdcI3izj.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112046UEz23Y5rAmheV9ks.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112047L9obe5lUcA3O1JD8.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112047A80EtbBc91ZgQ3dq.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112048EDpt3hufXPdGlskZ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\twrist band by Layer\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这条手腕带可以采集“碳足迹（carbon footprints）”，即我们呼出的二氧化碳，并连上手机 app，来自英国伦敦的设计事务所 Layer。设计的灵感源于我们对健身消耗的记录，可以帮助使用者分析日常习惯，选择更健康的居住环境。不过，带彩色圆点的石制手链本身就很独特了。<a href=\"http://layerdesign.com/projects/worldbeing/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112048yGvqKx2dhTiYfbwH.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112049yRFukTGi3dHKJL91.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112049eZ5agBhNHLoAIXQG.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112049Gk4eQVXADBrTLMhi.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.45833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112050UEitpvzLYb8OmnBW.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.53333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}